However, today we are discussing safety due to the recent tragedy.
Reporters have been urged to change their daily routines.
Two seasoned journalists discuss which is safer: leaving the children at home or taking them with them to the office that was bombed in 2009.
Security experts have written three words on the blackboard at the front of the room: adversaries, neutrals, allies.
