The operating environment is constantly changing.
Mobile phones were not allowed in the room where the Riodoce safety training was held. A few days earlier, it had emerged that activists and journalists in Mexico were being monitored by spyware sold only to governments.
Outside the building, two policemen had sought shelter from the 40-degree heat under the shade of a tree.
